      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5082 - Ibn Mahbub narrated from Malik ibn Atiyyah from Abu Basir from Abu Abdullah (as) regarding a woman who accused a man (of adultery).\nImam (as) said: \"She is to be flogged eighty lashes.\""
